attributes.title: JUST NO❤️
attributes.review:
see..i got this app because i was not able to come to my favorite presidents rally as something came up(my rat wanted taco bell). For the first few days it was fine. but one day, MY PHONE WENT MISSING. I STARTED SEARCHING FOR IT EVERYWHERE. THEN I SAW IT. I LOOKED OUT THE WINDOW AND IT WAS FLYING. MY PHONE GREW WINGS BECAUSE OF THIS APP AND I AM NOT KIDDING😖😖😖😖. BUT THEN IT SLOWLY LANDED. i thought it was another app at first but NO😱😨😱😨😱😨😱! because as soon as i opened the flag and saw his amazing and glorious orange face, my rat that was sitting next to me died😭(rip❤️❤️). it almost seemed like the rat would rather die than look at a cheeto puff🧚‍♂️🧚‍♂️. i was still ok with this app till i got a call. it was my doctor telling me i had cancer😔 my body was IN A RUSH to die and so i ran screaming because i was T E R R I F I E D and ✨accidentally✨ ran over the american flag and trumps face(i am very sorry cheeto sir). i then deleted the app but my love for our president with a kindergarteners mindset will never die❤️. SUDDENLY, i got a call. my cancer was CURED. this app controls u if u have it😳. I was happy but then decided to warn other people about it. I unfortunately downloaded it again to write a review for you guys😪😻. APP STARTED CONTROLLING ME AGAIN and i am now on my way to the white house to run over our 💫educated💫president with a tractor🚜. rip sir u will always want to make us cry and die from within. and because of me❤️, your life was ✨very very short✨ and even though it seemed too long to me, i’m sure you wanted to ruin the country more 🧚‍♂️😻. I have decided to throw a huge P A R T Y🥳🥳 in honor of you(and your death which took a while but finally happened)💝. 
I would also like to say one more thing: OOPS MY BAD! I 💕totally💕 did not mean to do that. and SINCE THIS APP DID THAT. DO. NOT. GET. IT. I have also seen other people say this app makes ur phone grow limbs. and unless u want your phone to kill u because ur ✨republican✨(which is very reasonable), I strongly recommend you do not get this app❤️🥺.
